713627f-a.title: Manhattan: 52nd Street (West) - 10th Avenue
713627f-a.text:
447 West 52nd Street, north side, east of Tenth Avenue. This is a one-story frame shack used as a stable.
1932.
J. Clarence Davies Collection, Museum of the City of New York.
Negative No. 593
